					"“Nah... The two of them would much rather hang out with kids their own age. So I usually just end up celebrating with my friends.”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					name = {"礼"},
					"“啊啊……他们两个比起我似乎还是跟同世代的孩子一起比较开心……总是会丢下我跟朋友一起去初诣……”",
					{"rt2"},
